        Maps the specified row and column to the specified value in the table. Neither the row nor the column nor the value can be null
        The value can be retrieved by calling the get method with a row and column that is equal to the original row and column.
        Parameters:
        r - the table row
        c - the table column
        v - the value
        Throws:
